{
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "title": "MS Clínica - About Section",
  "type": "section",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "about_section",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "layout": "boxed",
        "background_background": "classic",
        "background_color": "#FFFFFF",
        "padding": {
          "unit": "px",
          "top": 80,
          "right": 0,
          "bottom": 80,
          "left": 0,
          "sizes": {
            "tablet": {
              "top": 60,
              "bottom": 60
            },
            "mobile": {
              "top": 40,
              "bottom": 40
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "about_header_container",
          "elType": "container",
          "settings": {
            "content_width": "full",
            "flex_direction": "column",
            "flex_align_items": "center",
            "margin": {
              "unit": "px",
              "bottom": 60,
              "sizes": {
                "mobile": {
                  "bottom": 40
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "about_title",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Sobre Nós",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "color": "#2D2D2D",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_size": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 42,
                  "sizes": {
                    "tablet": 36,
                    "mobile": 30
                  }
                },
                "typography_font_weight": "600",
                "align": "center",
                "margin": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "bottom": 15
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "about_divider",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "divider",
              "settings": {
                "width": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 80
                },
                "weight": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 4
                },
                "color": "#D4A84B",
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "about_content_container",
          "elType": "container",
          "settings": {
            "content_width": "full",
            "flex_direction": "row",
            "flex_align_items": "center",
            "gap": {
              "unit": "px",
              "size": 60,
              "sizes": {
                "mobile": {
                  "size": 40
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "about_text_column",
              "elType": "container",
              "settings": {
                "flex_basis": "50%",
                "flex_direction": "column"
              },
              "elements": [
                {
                  "id": "about_text_content",
                  "elType": "widget",
                  "widgetType": "text-editor",
                  "settings": {
                    "editor": "<p>A <strong>MS Clínica (Malheiro & Sampaio)</strong> é uma clínica multidisciplinar localizada na Maia, Porto, dedicada a proporcionar cuidados de saúde premium em diversas áreas.</p><p>Com uma equipa altamente qualificada e experiente, combinamos tecnologia de ponta com atendimento personalizado para garantir os melhores resultados aos nossos pacientes.</p><p>Oferecemos uma vasta gama de serviços que abrangem <strong>Medicina Estética</strong>, <strong>Medicina Dentária</strong>, <strong>Terapias & Especialidades</strong> e <strong>Medicina Integrativa</strong>, sempre com foco no bem-estar integral de cada pessoa.</p><p>Na MS Clínica, acreditamos que cuidar de si é um investimento no seu futuro. Venha experimentar <em>o luxo de se sentir bem</em>.</p>",
                    "text_color": "#555555",
                    "typography_typography": "custom",
                    "typography_font_size": {
                      "unit": "px",
                      "size": 16
                    },
                    "typography_line_height": {
                      "unit": "em",
                      "size": 1.8
                    }
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "about_image_column",
              "elType": "container",
              "settings": {
                "flex_basis": "50%",
                "flex_direction": "column"
              },
              "elements": [
                {
                  "id": "about_image_placeholder",
                  "elType": "widget",
                  "widgetType": "image",
                  "settings": {
                    "image": {
                      "url": "",
                      "id": ""
                    },
                    "image_size": "large",
                    "border_border": "dashed",
                    "border_width": {
                      "unit": "px",
                      "size": 2
                    },
                    "border_color": "#D4A84B",
                    "border_radius": {
                      "unit": "px",
                      "size": 10
                    },
                    "background_background": "classic",
                    "background_color": "#F5F5F5",
                    "padding": {
                      "unit": "px",
                      "top": 80,
                      "right": 40,
                      "bottom": 80,
                      "left": 40
                    },
                    "caption_text": "Imagem da Clínica",
                    "caption_position": "center"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "about_image_fallback",
                  "elType": "widget",
                  "widgetType": "icon",
                  "settings": {
                    "selected_icon": {
                      "value": "fas fa-hospital-alt",
                      "library": "fa-solid"
                    },
                    "icon_color": "#D4A84B",
                    "icon_size": {
                      "unit": "px",
                      "size": 80
                    },
                    "align": "center"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "responsive": {
    "mobile": {
      "about_content_container": {
        "flex_direction": "column"
      },
      "column_basis": "100%"
    }
  },
  "notes": "Substitua o placeholder da imagem por uma foto real da clínica MS. Recomenda-se imagem de alta qualidade mostrando as instalações ou equipa."
}
